00:10:18.052 --> 00:10:20.054
Me neither.

261
00:10:23.318 --> 00:10:25.320
I'm scared this means
you're gonna leave.

262
00:10:25.363 --> 00:10:28.192
Right now.
all it means is

263
00:10:28.236 --> 00:10:30.630
I am going home

264
00:10:30.673 --> 00:10:34.459
and pouring myself
a beautiful glass of wine.

265
00:10:34.503 --> 00:10:37.245
What is going on
with your computer?What?

266
00:10:38.725 --> 00:10:41.031
Whoa. whoa!
Someone's attacking my system.

267
00:10:41.075 --> 00:10:42.250
Who?

268
00:10:42.293 --> 00:10:43.599
I-I don't know.
I just managed

269
00:10:43.643 --> 00:10:45.470
to get past Viridipoint's
proxy firewall.

270
00:10:45.514 --> 00:10:47.124
So it's someone
from V-Point?

271
00:10:47.168 --> 00:10:49.170
I don't think so.
I think this is someone else.

272
00:10:51.085 --> 00:10:52.477
"Back off"?

273
00:10:52.521 --> 00:10:54.175
No. no. no.

274
00:10:54.218 --> 00:10:56.481
I'm locked out.

275
00:10:56.525 --> 00:10:58.309
I've been hijacked.

276
00:11:00.268 --> 00:11:02.662
You want a glass
of wine. too?

277
00:11:08.189 --> 00:11:09.364
Mrs. Rice.

278
00:11:09.407 --> 00:11:10.931
it's just pretrial
motions today.

279
00:11:10.974 --> 00:11:12.193
You don't have to be here.

280
00:11:12.236 --> 00:11:13.498
Oh. I'm here. every day.

281
00:11:13.542 --> 00:11:14.891
You don't have
to worry about that.

282
00:11:14.935 --> 00:11:17.241
Hey. You're from
TAC. right?

283
00:11:17.285 --> 00:11:20.157
Vijay Paterson.
counsel for Viridipoint.

284
00:11:20.201 --> 00:11:22.682
We're in 1138.
Motion's been reassigned.

285
00:11:22.725 --> 00:11:23.987
Reassigned? What judge?

286
00:11:24.031 --> 00:11:26.642
Preston.Preston? Never heard of him.

287
00:11:26.686 --> 00:11:28.818
It's a her.

288
00:11:28.862 --> 00:11:31.952
She's new. Just appointed.

289
00:11:31.995 --> 00:11:33.257
Is new good?

290
00:11:33.301 --> 00:11:35.564
We're gonna find out. Your Honor.

291
00:11:35.607 --> 00:11:37.740
my client understands
the emotions involved.

292
00:11:37.784 --> 00:11:41.135
but the fact remains.
Viridipoint had no duty of care

293
00:11:41.178 --> 00:11:42.527
