294
00:11:42.571 --> 00:11:45.748
That duty rested solely
with the NYPD officers

295
00:11:45.792 --> 00:11:46.793
at the scene.

296
00:11:46.836 --> 00:11:48.882
As such. we ask
the court to grant

297
00:11:48.925 --> 00:11:50.405
our motion to dismiss.

298
00:11:50.448 --> 00:11:53.103
Your Honor. Viridipoint's
facial recognition software

299
00:11:53.147 --> 00:11:54.757
falsely identified

300
00:11:54.801 --> 00:11:57.325
Corey Rice
as a dangerous suspect.

301
00:11:57.368 --> 00:11:59.893
Mr. Rice's fatal shooting
at the hands of police

302
00:11:59.936 --> 00:12:02.896
who relied on the accuracy
of that software proves

303
00:12:02.939 --> 00:12:04.288
conclusively that

304
00:12:04.332 --> 00:12:06.421
the duty of care rests
with Viridipoint.

305
00:12:06.464 --> 00:12:08.945
Isn't it the NYPD's job

306
00:12:08.989 --> 00:12:10.599
to properly train its officers

307
00:12:10.642 --> 00:12:12.775
