the shooter.

376
00:14:58.201 --> 00:15:00.116
That is a novel argument.

377
00:15:01.639 --> 00:15:03.424
I'd like to see if you
can make that stick.

378
00:15:03.467 --> 00:15:06.079
Motion to dismiss
