393
00:15:36.022 --> 00:15:38.067
What do you want to do?

394
00:15:38.111 --> 00:15:38.981
Pay.

395
00:15:39.025 --> 00:15:40.330
Money's the only thing

396
00:15:40.374 --> 00:15:41.810
