397
00:15:41.853 --> 00:15:43.290
How much?

398
00:15:43.333 --> 00:15:45.683
20.000.

399
00:15:45.727 --> 00:15:48.599
You can have five.
and get a receipt.

400
00:15:48.643 --> 00:15:50.253
No problem.

401
00:15:50.297 --> 00:15:52.342
Hackers love
to give receipts.

402
00:15:54.779 --> 00:15:56.999
Chunk called. I will adjust
the juror algorithm

403
00:15:57.043 --> 00:15:59.001
