new cause of action.

404
00:15:59.045 --> 00:16:01.003
Deceptive trade
practices. right?

405
00:16:01.047 --> 00:16:03.658
That's what
he sold them on.

406
00:16:03.701 --> 00:16:05.181
I need you to help me

407
00:16:05.225 --> 00:16:07.357
