while we're working on this one.

409
00:16:09.490 --> 00:16:11.492
I won't walk out on you
in the middle of a case.

410
00:16:11.535 --> 00:16:13.189
Give me some credit.

411
00:16:13.233 --> 00:16:14.886
Well. I would have
before yesterday.

412
00:16:14.930 --> 00:16:16.714
All right. we have worked
together for 12 years.

413
00:16:16.758 --> 00:16:18.890
I know. Oh. is that
Mr. Lena checking in?

414
00:16:18.934 --> 00:16:20.718
All due respect.
that's none of your business.

415
00:16:20.762 --> 00:16:22.285
Okay.

416
00:16:22.329 --> 00:16:24.505
Listen. I think we can handle
this one without you.

417
00:16:24.548 --> 00:16:27.899
You got a lot going on.
You got a new job to consider.

418
00:16:27.943 --> 00:16:29.945
a lot on your plate.
We got this one.

419
00:16:29.989 --> 00:16:33.035
I... Who'll run the board?

420
00:16:33.079 --> 00:16:35.255
I will.

421
00:16:40.347 --> 00:16:42.827
Hey.
Hi.

422
00:16:45.134 --> 00:16:47.397
Is everything
all right?
Yup.

423
00:16:49.356 --> 00:16:51.662
Look. if Benny's
office is an issue.

424
00:16:51.706 --> 00:16:53.751
I can find
another place.

425
00:16:53.795 --> 00:16:55.753
The office
is not the problem.

426
00:16:55.797 --> 00:16:58.060
Well. Jason mentioned that

427
00:16:58.104 --> 00:17:00.758
