and that you've been unhappy.

428
00:17:00.802 --> 00:17:03.283
At least he heard me
this time.

429
00:17:04.980 --> 00:17:06.938
He needs you.

430
00:17:06.982 --> 00:17:08.940
TAC cannot work
without you.

431
00:17:08.984 --> 00:17:10.768
and he knows it.
Really?

432
00:17:10.812 --> 00:17:13.771
Is that why he just
pulled me from the case?

433
00:17:13.815 --> 00:17:15.599
Well...
I never said

434
00:17:15.643 --> 00:17:17.079
he's not an
idiot. but...

435
00:17:17.123 --> 00:17:18.950
Don't you dare say that
his heart's in the right place.

436
00:17:18.994 --> 00:17:22.606
He has been dismissing me
and my ideas for months.

437
00:17:22.650 --> 00:17:25.261
Look. I love TAC.

438
00:17:25.305 --> 00:17:27.133
I helped build it.

439
00:17:27.176 --> 00:17:29.570
It's my home.

440
00:17:29.613 --> 00:17:31.615
I want to stay. but...

441
00:17:31.659 --> 00:17:33.095
