444
00:17:49.285 --> 00:17:50.808
Excuse me.

445
00:17:50.852 --> 00:17:52.941
Hey. um...

446
00:17:52.984 --> 00:17:55.639
I'm having
computer problems.

447
00:17:55.683 --> 00:17:58.947
Have you tried unplugging it
and plugging it back in?

448
00:17:58.990 --> 00:18:01.384
I think it's a little more
complicated than that.

449
00:18:01.428 --> 00:18:03.082
Maybe Tidal can help?

450
00:18:04.300 --> 00:18:06.781
That's you. right?

451
00:18:06.824 --> 00:18:08.696
I can't help you.

452
00:18:08.739 --> 00:18:10.524
You shut down my system

453
00:18:10.567 --> 00:18:12.917
because I found a gap
in Viridipoint's AI firewall.

454
00:18:12.961 --> 00:18:14.658
I need that gap to stay open.

455
00:18:19.272 --> 00:18:20.795
$5.000.

456
00:18:22.405 --> 00:18:24.233
It's yours...

457
00:18:24.277 --> 00:18:25.713
if you leave me alone.

458
00:18:26.627 --> 00:18:29.108
Oh. I'm gonna need... 

459
00:18:29.151 --> 00:18:32.241
...$20.000 for that
to be worth my while.

460
00:18:32.285 --> 00:18:34.025
I don't have that.

461
00:18:34.069 --> 00:18:36.898
Then you still got a problem.

462
00:18:36.941 --> 00:18:38.508
Sorry. soccer mom.

463
00:18:38.552 --> 00:18:41.903
Uh. for the record.
my son does not play soccer.

464
00:18:41.946 --> 00:18:43.426
and I pulled off
the Whisper Mode hack

465
00:18:43.470 --> 00:18:44.862
while you were still
dancing on your bed

466
00:18:44.906 --> 00:18:46.690
under a poster of Avril Lavigne.

467
00:18:46.734 --> 00:18:49.040
so bite me.

468
00:18:50.477 --> 00:18:52.218
Yo.

469
00:18:52.261 --> 00:18:55.177
No way you pulled
off Whisper Mode.

470
00:18:55.221 --> 00:18:56.396
Oh. yeah. I did.

471
00:18:56.439 --> 00:18:57.745
Prove it.

472
00:18:57.788 --> 00:18:59.660
The point was
to remain anonymous.

473
00:18:59.703 --> 00:19:02.271
I didn't keep a bunch
of hard evidence against myself.

474
00:19:02.315 --> 00:19:03.838
Okay. well I know
a little bit about it.

475
00:19:03.881 --> 00:19:07.146
Tell me something
you can't read on Wikipedia.

476
00:19:08.364 --> 00:19:10.323
Um...

477
00:19:10.366 --> 00:19:12.020
Okay.

478
00:19:13.282 --> 00:19:14.892
everyone thinks I hacked

479
00:19:14.936 --> 00:19:18.461
the FBI. DHS. and GCHQ.
but I also hacked NASA.

480
00:19:18.505 --> 00:19:21.247
That's not generally known
because it was classified.

481
00:19:21.290 --> 00:19:23.205
Respect.

482
00:19:23.249 --> 00:19:25.816
Does that mean you'll back off
and let me do my work?

483
00:19:25.860 --> 00:19:28.297
Won't matter
if I back off.
Why not?

484
00:19:28.341 --> 00:19:30.821
That hole in the firewall
you were working?

485
00:19:30.865 --> 00:19:32.562
Viridipoint plugged it
up this morning.

486
00:19:32.606 --> 00:19:34.999
Great.

487
00:19:35.043 --> 00:19:36.131
I might know

488
00:19:36.175 --> 00:19:39.482
some other ways
into their servers.

489
00:19:39.526 --> 00:19:40.831
I could show you.

490
00:19:40.875 --> 00:19:43.269
Testing.

491
00:19:43.312 --> 00:19:44.879
Testing one. two. three.

492
00:19:44.922 --> 00:19:47.708
Rubber baby buggy bumper.
Rubber baby buggy bumper.

493
00:19:47.751 --> 00:19:50.537
Bull? Please stop.

494
00:19:50.580 --> 00:19:52.234
Just warming up my lips.

495
00:19:52.278 --> 00:19:54.976
So. has our data scientist
taken the stand yet?

496
00:19:55.019 --> 00:19:57.848
So help me God.Just sworn in.

497
00:19:57.892 --> 00:19:59.937
Now. keep him out of the weeds.

498
00:19:59.981 --> 00:20:01.243
Nothing loses a jury faster

499
00:20:01.287 --> 00:20:03.985
than five-dollar words
and tech jargon.

500
00:20:04.028 --> 00:20:06.335
Dr. Gasden.

501
00:20:06.379 --> 00:20:08.642
you are an expert
in artificial intelligence.

502
00:20:08.685 --> 00:20:11.993
particularly with
facial recognition. correct?

503
00:20:12.036 --> 00:20:13.212
Yes.

504
00:20:13.255 --> 00:20:16.432
Doctor. I'd like to show you
a photograph

505
00:20:16.476 --> 00:20:17.781
of some footage from the

506
00:20:17.825 --> 00:20:19.740
security camera
that the police used

507
00:20:19.783 --> 00:20:21.220
to falsely identify

508
00:20:21.263 --> 00:20:24.048
Corey Rice
as a suspect. Now.

509
00:20:24.092 --> 00:20:26.747
in your expert opinion.

510
00:20:26.790 --> 00:20:29.053
is this footage conducive

511
00:20:29.097 --> 00:20:32.535
