using facial recognition?

512
00:20:32.579 --> 00:20:34.276
No.

513
00:20:34.320 --> 00:20:37.540
The dark lighting
and obscured facial features

514
00:20:37.584 --> 00:20:39.542
in that recording are...

515
00:20:39.586 --> 00:20:41.283
far from ideal.

516
00:20:41.327 --> 00:20:43.503
Given those conditions.

517
00:20:43.546 --> 00:20:46.332
the accuracy would only be
somewhere between...

518
